            <title>[CASSANDRA-17866] Fix potential test flake in MixedModeMessageForwardTest</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-17866</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This test will occasionally fail because there are no guarantees that the messaging service will be connected before the test tries to send the mutation request.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Given that this test is checking that &lt;tt&gt;FWD_FRM&lt;/tt&gt; is being deserialized correctly, we can just wait until a &lt;tt&gt;CL.ALL&lt;/tt&gt; request succeeds once to make sure messaging connections are established and then run the insert test.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
